props.title: Gold
props.description: This is our level three sunbed. You have an option to lay down or stand up. These beds have a higher level of UVB to activate the tanning process.

props.title: Elevate Your Tan with Gold Level Beds
props.content: Experience the ultimate tanning session with our Level Three Gold sunbeds at Ohana Sun Tanning. Designed for both comfort and effectiveness, these beds offer the flexibility of laying down or standing up, catering to your personal preference. With a higher level of UVB exposure, our Gold sunbeds accelerate the tanning process, ensuring a rich, golden glow in fewer sessions. The advanced technology of these beds not only enhances your tan but also helps achieve an even, long-lasting result. Ideal for those looking to deepen their tan or prepare for a special occasion, our Gold level service guarantees a rejuvenating experience in a relaxing environment. Let the warm rays of our Gold sunbeds help you shine brighter this season!

props.title: Benefits of Gold

benefits.title: Versatile Tanning Options
benefits.description: Choose between laying down or standing up, allowing for a personalized tanning experience to suit your comfort preference.

benefits.title: Enhanced UVB Exposure
benefits.description: Higher levels of UVB in the beds stimulate faster and more effective tanning, helping you achieve your desired skin tone more quickly.

benefits.title: Comfort and Convenience
benefits.description: The option to switch positions provides comfort and convenience, making your tanning session more enjoyable and adaptable to your needs.

benefits.title: Advanced Tanning Technology
benefits.description: Our level three sunbeds feature state-of-the-art technology designed to maximize tanning results while minimizing skin damage.

props.description: Discover the many advantages of choosing Gold at Ohana Sun Tanning

props.title: What Clients Say About Gold
props.description: Hear from satisfied clients who've experienced our Gold.

testimonials.name: Christina Sierra
testimonials.review: This place, these people, the tan I have the luxury of wearing now, all beyond exceptional. I was pleasantly surprised by their honesty. One night, I'd gone in for a custom spray tan (Gail is a wildly talented custom sprayer!) and I lost my gold bracelet I'd been wearing for 13 years upon removing for tanning process. Once I realized it was gone, I called to see if perhaps someone had found it. To my pleasant surprise, the lovely Ariel had found it on the floor & said to come on in & get it. A less honest person could have kept it, as there is some value there, but mostly sentimental for me. It was returned safely to me when I arrived...& for this I shall always remain their loyal (& grateful!) customer. Thank you Ariel & Image Sun, you guys are the BEST!

faqs.answer: The Gold service sunbed offers a higher level of UVB rays, which helps activate the tanning process more effectively, resulting in a deeper and faster tan.
faqs.question: What are the benefits of using the Gold service sunbed?

faqs.answer: Yes, the Gold service sunbed provides both options. You can choose to lay down or stand up based on your comfort and tanning preferences.
faqs.question: Can I choose between lying down and standing up?

faqs.answer: Typically, sessions range from 10 to 20 minutes, depending on your skin type and tanning goals. It's best to start with shorter sessions and gradually increase as needed.
faqs.question: How long should I stay in the Gold sunbed?

faqs.answer: While the Gold service is effective for many skin types, those with very fair or sensitive skin should consult with a professional to determine the best approach for tanning safely.
faqs.question: Is the Gold service suitable for all skin types?

faqs.answer: For optimal results, you can use the Gold sunbed 2 to 3 times a week. However, it's important to allow your skin to recover between sessions to avoid overexposure.
faqs.question: How often can I use the Gold sunbed?

faqs.answer: Using a tanning lotion or accelerator can enhance your tanning experience and results. It's recommended to apply a product specifically designed for sunbed use before your session.
faqs.question: Do I need to use any products before using the Gold sunbed?
